---
// Rendered by src/pages/nachbarn/[handle].astro (bad handle shape, or
// getPublicProfile() returns null — unknown handle or an anonymized
// tombstone) and src/pages/nachbarn/id/[userId].astro (invalid ObjectId, or
// getHandleForPublic() returns null). HTTP 200 keeps the URL stable +
// indexable-but-empty rather than a raw 404 — same pattern as the
// marketplace's ListingUnavailable.astro (src/components/marketplace/kiosk/
// states/ListingUnavailable.astro).
//
// v1 DE only — the kiosk i18n store lives in client-side localStorage and
// isn't reachable from an .astro file (SSR). Flip to a client-rendered
// Svelte island if multi-locale matters later.
//
// Design source: design/handoffs/design_handoff_profile/jsx/
// kiosk-profile-states.jsx (§03 "Profil nicht gefunden").
---

<div class="profile-notfound">
  <div class="profile-notfound__panel">
    <p class="profile-notfound__kicker">Nachbarschaft · Schillerkiez</p>
    <h1 class="profile-notfound__title">Diese Nachbarin ist nicht (mehr) hier.</h1>
    <a href="/" class="profile-notfound__cta">← zurück zum Forum</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .profile-notfound {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .profile-notfound__panel {
    background: var(--k-paper-warm, #f7f0de);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--k-rule, #c9c0a8);
    border-radius: var(--k-radius-md, 8px);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .profile-notfound__kicker {
    font-family: var(--k-font-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--k-ochre, #e8a53a);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .profile-notfound__title {
    font-family: var(--k-font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--k-ink, #1b1a17);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 22px;
  }

  .profile-notfound__cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--k-font-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--k-ink, #1b1a17);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: dashed;
    text-decoration-color: var(--k-rule, #c9c0a8);
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    transition: color 150ms ease;
  }

  .profile-notfound__cta:hover {
    color: var(--k-ochre, #e8a53a);
  }
</style>
